Black can meet} 13. Qh5+ {with} Qf7) 13. Qh5+ $1 {This provokative move, just
weaken Black's structure on the kingside} g6 14. Qd1 Bc5 15. Nc4 b5 16. Na5 Qd7
17. Be3 $1 {Dark squares are very weak and for White is good to exchange the
bishops.} Bb6 (17... Bxe3 18. fxe3 {opens the f-file}) 18. b4 $1 {fixing the
c5-square} O-O (18... c5 {doesn't solve the problems due to} 19. bxc5 Bxc5 20.
