) 24. Rxa7 Rxa7 25. Nxa7 {Black has no compensation for the two missing pawns.
The Chinese GM easily defends against Black's threats and win} f3 26. Qc6 Qe7
27. Nxb5 Kh8 28. g3 Qf7 29. Ra1 Ng5 30. Ra8 Qe7 31. h4 $5 Nh3+ 32. Kf1 e4 33.
Qxe4 1-0

