sequence is forced.} 24. Rxb3 Nc5 25. Bxc5 Rxc5 26. Rxb5 Rxc3 27. Qd2 Qc8 28.
Rb8 Qxb8 29. Qxc3 Bb6 {[%cal Ga7f2]} 30. Bd3 Bc5 31. Nh4 Qa7 {Black is even
