Bd5 Bb7 16. Nc3 $16 {Zubova,M (2089)-Aliyev,E (2161) Ordu 2017 (½-½, 83)})
11... Rb8 12. axb5 axb5 13. d5 Ne7 14. b4 g6 {Abdusattorov,N (2395)-Ponkratov,
P (2589) St Petersburg 2016 (0-1, 49)} 15. Qe2 Bg7 16. Na3 Ba6 (16... f5) 17.
Bd3) 11. Nbd2 Nb6 {Hoping for ...Bg4.} 12. h3 $1 Ng6 13. Nf1 {Black has no
