on b6 is completely misplaced.} Nh4 14. N1h2 Nxf3+ 15. Nxf3 Bd7 16. b3 c5 17.
dxc5 $6 (17. a4 $1 $16) 17... dxc5 18. Qd6 $6 (18. a4 $1 $14) 18... Rc8 19.
Nxe5 Bb5 $2 (19... Bxh3 $1 $11 20. Nxf7 Rxf7 21. Qxd8+ Rxd8 22. e5 (22. gxh3
