Rxa8 Qxa8 21. dxe5 dxe5 22. b3 Nc8 23. Nh2 Nd6 {Liepold,S - Lipok,C Germany
2014}) (19. b3 bxa4 20. bxa4 a5 21. dxe5 {This exchange mostly favours Black.
Now, Black has enough space he is already planning to occupy the c5-square
