24. Qxb3 Kg8 {, and Black has no problems.}) 21... dxe5 22. Bb3 Qe7 23. Be3
Nfd7 24. h4 $6 {White pushes too hard.} ({More to the point was} 24. Qc2 Rab8
25. Qa2 Rf8 {with mutual chances.}) 24... Ba6 25. h5 Nc4 26. Bxc4 Bxc4 {
